{"tid":1053682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角菲傭疑受情困墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-03-09T09:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T09:28:14.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90d1593452ab9b5584ba6444f9553522c2b838d0","tid":1053682,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"北角健康村康勝閣，中午12時38分，女戶主報案指其32歲菲傭由寓所廚房墮下，跌落天井，昏迷不醒，消防員到場升起雲梯，將菲傭抬救到地面，惟救護員證實她當場不治，警方正調查事件，據悉，菲傭疑受情困而尋死。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ueSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=c4c488d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190309/59348873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348873&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ueSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=4991f2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348873&h=d104e17f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190309/59348873</a>"},{"pid":"c226536657543d0f5e380ddb07e4a1807933e31d","tid":1053682,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b2b923966a5648325b0e726c59dffbf7af4501","tid":1053682,"uid":29982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:07:54.000Z","msg":"跌幾成"},{"pid":"021f7da2099098f370407201a53187d32cb16aa6","tid":1053682,"uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,